  "questionProse": [
    "HTMLで `<dd>` 要素は何を表しますか？"
  ],
  "explanationProse": [
    "The [`<dd>` element](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dd) defines a description, definition, or value in a description list, used within `<dl>` tags to pair with `<dt>` (_Description Term_).\n\nThis is useful when showing key-value data. Profile information, Settings, and Stats are a common examples."
  ]
}
